  m_text: What do you think Alex? This could be a good time to bond with your classmates.
    And who knows? This might even lead to new opportunities in the future! Pero,
    it could also be better to just save some money for your Ipon.It also never hurts
    to be more prepared for any unfortunate situation that could happen!
