  m_text: "The morning light seeps through the curtains as Alex stretches and grabs
    her phone. A notification pops up \u2014 allowance received. A smile forms; the
    first official step into college life has just begun. She opens her budgeting
    app, thinking of needs, savings, and maybe a little treat before the chaos starts.
    One week left \u2014 time to plan it right"
