  m_text: "The campus buzzes with energy as Alex hurries into class, coffee in hand
    and eyes still half\u2011closed. The lecture begins \u2014 long, steady, and
    a little too comfy. Before she knows it, her head dips, and the professor\u2019s
    voice turns into white noise. A quiet chuckle from her seatmate snaps her awake
    just in time.\r\n\r\nBy lunch, the mood shifts. Alex and friends gather around
    a crowded table at the cafeteria, trading stories and fries. Laughter bounces
    between bites, melting away the morning\u2019s stress. When the sun starts to
    set, she packs her things, waves goodbye, and heads home \u2014 tired, but content.
    Another ordinary day that somehow feels like progress"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -1582481626441873841, guid: 75a7dcceb17caec49b06beab28e14a39, type: 2}
